title: 2nd floor, Great location on the Edge of Uptown
posting_body: ['Welcome to your new home, The Edge of Uptown Apartments!', 'Make an appointment for a tour today!', '(3D virtual tours and availability can be found at: <URL> )', 'Included with rent :Heat and trash', 'You pay: Electric, sewer, and water.', "Amenities include: State of the art Fitness Center (Open 24/7) and Tanning Room, an upscale Party Room with Smart Tv, Private Theatre/Game room, Conference room, Business center, and lastly a lovely Guest Suite so you're out of town guests can stay with you in the building rather than find a motel!", 'Parking Options: Parking Garage (additional $70 per month)', 'Parking Lot, and Street Parking.', 'Apartment Amenities: Controlled Access doors, Ceiling Fans, Dishwasher, Garbage Disposal, Spacious Closets, Air Conditioning All apartments come Internet and Cable-ready.', 'Visit us on our website at <URL>', 'Our professional and friendly staff is eager to assist you 6 days a week!', '(Monday-Saturday)', 'While our On-Call Maintenance staff is available 7 days a week!', 'Call now to make an appointment!', "Our office hours are Monday-Friday 9:00am - 6:00pm and Saturday's from 10:00am - 3:00pm.", '*Non-Refundable application fee is $40/adult (all adults must apply)', '*We do Credit Checks* Must have satisfactory Rental History', '*Income: Gross monthly income (before taxes) must be minimum of 2.5 times the monthly rent.', '*We do Criminal Background Checks.', "*Rental applications may be subject to GOLDMARK'S criminal criteria"]
